        {
            "title": "金價升穿3000美元後回軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金價突破3000美元關口，關稅戰引發經濟不確定，避險需求推高金價。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"金價 (Shutterstock圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20170226_FI_Gold_FB_source-web_-4-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"金價 (Shutterstock圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20170226_FI_Gold_FB_source-web_-4-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">金價 (Shutterstock圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">現貨金高見每盎司3004.86美元，升近0.6%，較早時回落0.1%，徘徊2984美元附近。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期金高見3017.1美元，收報3001.1美元，升9.8美元，升幅0.3%，本周累計升約3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14777495-%e9%87%91%e5%83%b9%e5%8d%87%e7%a9%bf3000%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e5%be%8c%e5%9b%9e%e8%bb%9f-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250304_FI_GOLD_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-15 11:10:39",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股周五反彈約2%　道指一周跌逾3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股3大指數顯著反彈近2%或以上，但全星期累計仍下跌，市場持續關注美國總統特朗普關稅政策影響。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241219_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241219_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯工業平均指數重上41000點水平，最多升逾710點，收市報41488點，升674點，升幅1.65%，結束4日跌勢。大幅高開244點後，尾段升幅最多擴大至714點，最高報41528點；</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標普500指數收報5638點，升117點，升幅2.13%，標指曾漲2.24%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數收報17754點，升451點，升幅2.61%，一度上揚2.72%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">反映中國概念股表現的金龍指數反彈2.69%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金龍中國指數微彈0.2%</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">總結全星期，道指累計跌3.1%，連跌兩星期；標普500指數及納指都跌逾2%，兩者都連跌4星期。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股造好，輝達(Nvidia)收市股價漲5.3%，為表現最強道指成份股，本周累計反彈8%；博通、AMD、高通升逾2%至3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其他科技股亦升，Netflix升3.1%，Meta升3%，特斯拉(Tesla)抽高3.9%，本周累計滑落4.8%，為連跌8周。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金礦股受追捧，Newmont股價揚1.3%。金融股造好，高盛、摩根大通和美國運通升幅3.1%至3.5%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14777484-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e5%91%a8%e4%ba%94%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88%e7%b4%842%e3%80%80%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240730_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-15 10:55:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英德股市創一周新高  德股升近1.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲股市造好，德國股市表現較好，銀行及國防股上升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市反彈1.15%，報546點，本周累計仍然錄得超過1%跌幅。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國保守派陣營領袖默茨提出的財政改革方案，獲得綠黨支持，國會下星期二將就債務協議進行表決。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230711-094811_20191002_EUSTOCK_-source-ap_-1-1-2.png.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230711-094811_20191002_EUSTOCK_-source-ap_-1-1-2.png.webp\"/>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英德股市創1星期新高，德國DAX指數曾升穿23000點關口，收市報22986點，升419點，升幅1.86%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數收報8632點，升89點，升幅1.05%，連升3日。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數重上8000點，收報8028點，升90點，升幅1.13%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英法德股市本周累計跌0.1%至1.1%，法股跌幅最大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報38655點，走高1.73%或655點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報13005點，上漲1.43%或183點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國2月消費物價指數(CPI)終值持平，按年升0.8%，兩者與預期相同；德國2月CPI終值按月升0.4%，按年升2.3%，兩者均符合預期。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14777489-%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6%e8%bf%911-9%e3%80%80%e5%8f%97%e6%83%a0%e6%96%bc%e5%be%b7%e5%9c%8b%e8%b2%a1%e6%94%bf%e6%94%b9%e9%9d%a9%e9%80%b2%e5%b1%95",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-15 10:40:38",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
